text: Autreville-sur-la-Renne is a commune in the Haute-Marne department in northeastern France. Between 1972 and 2012, the commune Lavilleneuve-au-Roi was part of Autreville-sur-la-Renne. == Related pages == * Communes of the Haute-Marne department == References == Category:Communes in Haute-Marne
title: Autreville-sur-la-Renne
